The Floating Island

An island suspended in mid-air, tethered by vines. A crystal ball on a velvet cushion flickers with moving images - scenes from another world, filmed with actors and game engines.

# floating-island-episodes

Episodes

Filmed scenes from the Aetherion world - voice acting, game engine footage, original score.

